{"tid":2298490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美少將傳訪台為拜登收風","createTime":"2020-11-24T05:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T06:29:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab1c81d136bf983bd498accbbdd265a7d850735","tid":2298490,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:46:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201124/XETVUM2VOZHM7HWGX4AO3HEZCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201124%2FXETVUM2VOZHM7HWGX4AO3HEZCM%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=42d081cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201124%2FXETVUM2VOZHM7HWGX4AO3HEZCM%2F&h=d0740496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201124/XETVUM2VOZHM7HWGX4AO3HEZCM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美少將傳訪台為拜登收風<br />\n<br />\n一架隸屬美國軍方的行政專機前晚降落台北松山機場，有傳是負責亞太地區情報的美國海軍二星少將史達曼訪台兩天，回國後將向美國總統推定當選人拜登的國安團隊簡報亞太情報。中國外交部重申，中方堅決反對任何形式的美台官方往來和軍事聯繫，並將根據形勢發展做出正當、必要反應。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：列「軍民融合」黑名單 中航工業上榜  美擬再封殺華89間企業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XwjfS2DEkZtNddg_u6zGphO-DdE=/945x721/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PBWQ2QCVUBGFVN7DRGBHOBEGWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXwjfS2DEkZtNddg_u6zGphO-DdE%3D%2F945x721%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPBWQ2QCVUBGFVN7DRGBHOBEGWI.jpg&h=c229fa87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有傳秘密訪台的官員為美軍印太司令部情報處長史達曼。 路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美台不回應 外交部譴責<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述包括一名台灣官員在內的兩名匿名知情者稱，秘密抵台訪問的是美軍印太司令部情報處長二星少將史達曼。台灣蘋果新聞網引述消息指，史達曼此行目的是「情報資產」，對亞太地區的的情報部署及整合進行專案報告，並將向拜登的國安團隊簡報。在前總統馬英九任內，美方曾派遣二星將領到台灣公務旅行。<br />\n<br />\n美國和台灣的國防部都對消息不予置評。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，台灣總統蔡英文昨出席亞洲自由民主聯盟大會開幕發表演說，指在疫情下民主面對其中一個挑戰就是假訊息，台灣經驗就是民主價值在面對極權勢力之戰的最佳示範。她不點名批評中共，指資訊操縱一直以來是獨裁國家用來破壞民主國家的的工具，這種令人不安的趨勢成為對台灣的常態威脅。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"8f51526f1af5f8c9302e0977b26a2e576fdd3df5","tid":2298490,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"Help ar joe to ask for 幻幻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbb1321cb1bb5b789ad3dc3f91b87df3d7431d9","tid":2298490,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"睇錯美少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ac0d5771e42c2849be8f674c318f17e600d55d","tid":2298490,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"飛中國幫拜登攞料點知去錯中華民國"},{"pid":"317062e5d72783da73eccca84c91c248e932bd20","tid":2298490,"uid":233905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f51526f1af5f8c9302e0977b26a2e576fdd3df5","tid":2298490,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"Help ar joe to ask for 幻幻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:02:37.000Z","msg":"去新北市視察<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49632de7d68d7d61219a5e768db86c9073d88428","tid":2298490,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317062e5d72783da73eccca84c91c248e932bd20","tid":2298490,"uid":233905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f51526f1af5f8c9302e0977b26a2e576fdd3df5","tid":2298490,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"Help ar joe to ask for 幻幻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:02:37.000Z","msg":"去新北市視察<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"可以玩得好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a